             were indicted for <rs id="t18200918-161-off929" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18200918-161-off929" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200918-161-off929" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18200918-161-cd930" type="crimeDate">19th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200918-161-off929 t18200918-161-cd930"></join>, 90 lbs. of lead, value 12 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200918-161-victim1698" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Harding
                        <interp inst="t18200918-161-victim1698" type="surname" value="Harding"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18200918-161-victim1698" type="given" value="John"></interp>
